# ===========================================
# OBI-WAITER CMS - ENVIRONMENT CONFIGURATION
# ===========================================
# 
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file to create your environment file:
#    - Development: cp env.example env.development
#    - Staging:     cp env.example env.staging
#    - Production:  cp env.example env.production
# 
# 2. Replace all placeholder values with your actual configuration
# 
# 3. Never commit actual environment files to version control
#    (they are in .gitignore)
# 
# ===========================================

# ===========================================
# ENVIRONMENT SETTINGS
# ===========================================
